{"context": "总结 RIOM 是由放射疗法引起的正常口腔黏膜组织损伤，发病率高，虽然有一定的自限性，但在疾病发 生的过程中， 患者往往十分痛苦， 甚至无法进食， 导致患者营养不良， 甚至会中断RT 等。", "spans": [{"start": 3, "end": 7, "label": "Condition", "text": "RIOM"}, {"start": 5, "end": 7, "label": "Condition", "text": "OM"}, {"start": 32, "end": 36, "label": "Agent", "text": "放疗射线"}, {"start": 65, "end": 72, "label": "Damage", "text": "DNA 断裂"}, {"start": 76, "end": 79, "label": "Agent", "text": "ROS"}, {"start": 84, "end": 88, "label": "Factor", "text": "炎症因子"}, {"start": 89, "end": 91, "label": "Treatment", "text": "RT"}]}
