{"context": "(5) 小结 综合分析表明，电离辐射后，受损细胞首先出现 DNA 损伤及 ROS 的大量释放。DNA 损伤主要以 DNA 双链断裂为主，未能正确、及时修复的受损细胞会上调TGF-β、NF-kB 以及 p53 等信号通路，共同 诱导细胞凋亡，而高度激活 NF-kB 通路后，其下游通路也上调，释放大量炎症因子(TNF-α、IL-1β、IL-6 等)及趋化因子， 导致炎性细胞的累积和上皮基底细胞死亡， 进一步加重黏膜损伤。ROS 的大量释放会激 活 p53/p21 CIP 1、mTOR 信号通路和 p16 INK 4a/Rb 调节通路，诱导细胞周期停滞、细胞衰老，而炎性细 胞的累积又会正反馈作用于 ROS 的释放。", "spans": [{"start": 29, "end": 32, "label": "Molecule", "text": "DNA"}, {"start": 29, "end": 35, "label": "Damage", "text": "DNA 损伤"}, {"start": 37, "end": 40, "label": "Agent", "text": "ROS"}, {"start": 37, "end": 40, "label": "Agent", "text": "ROS"}, {"start": 37, "end": 40, "label": "Agent", "text": "ROS"}, {"start": 57, "end": 60, "label": "Molecule", "text": "DNA"}, {"start": 57, "end": 65, "label": "Damage", "text": "DNA 双链断裂"}, {"start": 85, "end": 90, "label": "Factor", "text": "TGF-β"}, {"start": 91, "end": 96, "label": "Factor", "text": "NF-kB"}, {"start": 100, "end": 103, "label": "Factor", "text": "p53"}, {"start": 105, "end": 109, "label": "Pathway", "text": "信号通路"}, {"start": 115, "end": 119, "label": "Process", "text": "细胞凋亡"}, {"start": 117, "end": 119, "label": "Process", "text": "凋亡"}, {"start": 126, "end": 131, "label": "Factor", "text": "NF-kB"}, {"start": 126, "end": 134, "label": "Pathway", "text": "NF-kB 通路"}, {"start": 149, "end": 153, "label": "Factor", "text": "炎症因子"}, {"start": 154, "end": 159, "label": "Factor", "text": "TNF-α"}, {"start": 160, "end": 165, "label": "Factor", "text": "IL-1β"}, {"start": 166, "end": 170, "label": "Factor", "text": "IL-6"}, {"start": 174, "end": 178, "label": "Factor", "text": "趋化因子"}, {"start": 182, "end": 186, "label": "Cell", "text": "炎性细胞"}, {"start": 182, "end": 186, "label": "Cell", "text": "炎性细胞"}, {"start": 190, "end": 196, "label": "Cell", "text": "上皮基底细胞"}, {"start": 192, "end": 196, "label": "Cell", "text": "基底细胞"}, {"start": 205, "end": 209, "label": "Damage", "text": "黏膜损伤"}, {"start": 224, "end": 227, "label": "Factor", "text": "p53"}, {"start": 224, "end": 237, "label": "Pathway", "text": "p53/p21 CIP 1"}, {"start": 238, "end": 242, "label": "Pathway", "text": "mTOR"}, {"start": 238, "end": 247, "label": "Pathway", "text": "mTOR 信号通路"}, {"start": 243, "end": 247, "label": "Pathway", "text": "信号通路"}, {"start": 249, "end": 252, "label": "Factor", "text": "p16"}, {"start": 249, "end": 262, "label": "Pathway", "text": "p16 INK 4a/Rb"}, {"start": 249, "end": 267, "label": "Pathway", "text": "p16 INK 4a/Rb 调节通路"}, {"start": 270, "end": 276, "label": "Process", "text": "细胞周期停滞"}, {"start": 277, "end": 281, "label": "Process", "text": "细胞衰老"}, {"start": 277, "end": 281, "label": "Process", "text": "细胞衰老"}, {"start": 280, "end": 284, "label": "Condition", "text": "RIOM"}, {"start": 293, "end": 297, "label": "Cell", "text": "衰老细胞"}]}
